scene.message:
Nanjo: "...when you're feeling{nl}
down, reach for Disparize~"{waitkey}...Blast it! I can't get{nl}
this jingle out of my head!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Better safe than{nl}
sorry!{wait_fr:37} ...as Yamaoka{nl}
used to often say.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Don't tell me you're{nl}
gonna make do with medicine?{nl}
Hey, let's go to the hospital{nl}
properly!{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: When I left home this{nl}
morning, I never imagined{nl}
something like this{nl}
would happen.{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: I wonder how bad{nl}
Sonomura's mom's injury is.{nl}
I hope it's not serious.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: For the shrine, go{nl}
south through the shopping{nl}
arcade, then keep heading{nl}
straight south.{waitkey}{clearbox}You turn down a narrow{nl}
street, so it might be a{nl}
little hard to find.{waitkey}{ret}

Shopkeeper: A St. Hermelin{nl}
student? You know my son?{nl}
Tadashi's his name!{waitkey}{clearbox}He's a hopeless lazybones,{nl}
but wouldn't you know, he's{nl}
gone and fallen for a really{nl}
cute girl!{waitkey}{clearbox}If a girl like that married{nl}
into the family, I'd be so{nl}
happy!{wait_fr:37} ...Hm? Oh, medicine?{nl}
Right, right.{waitkey}{ret}

Shopkeeper: Yes, welcome!{waitkey}{clearbox}Hey, have you met Tamaki?{nl}
I'm just so worried about{nl}
whether she's safe...{waitkey}I couldn't care less about{nl}
my own son, mind you!{nl}
...Hm? Oh, medicine? Right.{waitkey}{ret}

Customer: Hey, don't you{nl}
think it's strange too? That{nl}
Kaneda woman!{waitkey}I mean, getting that rich in{nl}
just half a year? It's fishy.{nl}
Definitely something off!{waitkey}{ret}

Shopkeeper: Oh? Here to see{nl}
my Tadashi, are you?{waitkey}That fool's off at his club{nl}
activities about now.{waitkey}{clearbox}Ahh, just once I'd love to{nl}
have a little spat with{nl}
Tamaki myself~♥{waitkey}{ret}

Shopkeeper: Oh? If it's{nl}
medicine you want, it's{nl}
over here!{waitkey}{ret}
